        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(openai): allow RFC 2544 fake-IP range for Realtime session requests",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- \\`fetchWithSsrFGuard\\` in \\`createOpenAIRealtimeSecret\\` was missing \\`policy: { allowRfc2544BenchmarkRange: true }\\`, causing the SSRF guard to block requests when proxy stacks (Clash, Surge, sing-box in TUN/fake-IP mode) resolve \\`api.openai.com\\` to the \\`198.18.0.0/15\\` special-use range.\n- The same opt-in already exists on other provider HTTP call paths; this fix closes the gap for the Realtime session-secret fetch path.\n- Added \\`policy\\` field assertions to both existing fetch-request checks in \\`realtime-voice-provider.test.ts\\` to prevent silent regression.\n\nCloses part of #56535.\n\n## Verification\n\n\\`\\`\\`\npnpm test extensions/openai/realtime-voice-provider.test.ts\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n- Test Files: 1 passed\n- Tests: 48 passed\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: SSRF guard blocks OpenAI Realtime session-secret requests when a TUN/fake-IP proxy resolves \\`api.openai.com\\` → \\`198.18.0.0/15\\`\nReal environment tested: macOS 15, OpenClaw 2026.5.25 (e3b9c11), Clash TUN/fake-IP mode active\nExact steps or command run after this patch: \\`OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=~/.openclaw-dev pnpm gateway:dev --port 19001\\`; open UI at \\`http://127.0.0.1:19001\\`; click Realtime Voice button\nEvidence after fix: \\`talk.client.create\\` RPC returned \\`ok: true\\` with \\`durationMs: 1711\\` (real network round-trip); audio streaming active with continuous \\`talk.session.appendAudio\\` calls all \\`ok: true\\`; AI responded in realtime — browser DevTools console: https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/87a884d2-2902-4915-ade1-99993691d5da\nObserved result after fix: Realtime voice session fully established; no SSRF block error; AI conversation active (see screenshots below)\nWhat was not tested: live Surge / sing-box environments (same code path, same policy opt-in)\n\n**Browser DevTools — session creation (`talk.client.create` → `ok: true`):**\n<img width=\"2880\" height=\"1626\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/87a884d2-2902-4915-ade1-99993691d5da\" />\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
